<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
     <h4>Loan Request</h4>
    <p> 
      This is to inform you that your Loan Request has been rejected.<br><br>
       1. <b>Member :-</b> <%= @loan_request.membership.employee.try(:first_name) %><%= @loan_request.membership.employee.try(:middle_name) %><%= @loan_request.membership.employee.try(:last_name) %><br><br>
       2. <b>Date :-</b> <%= @loan_request.date %><br><br>
       3. <b>Loan Type :-</b> <%= @loan_request.loan_type.try(:name) %><br><br>
       4. <b>EMI :-</b> <%= @loan_request.emi %><br><br>
       5. <b>Amount :-</b> <%= @loan_request.amount %>
       5. <b>No. of EMI :-</b> <%= @loan_request.no_of_emi %>
     </p>
  </body>
</html>